data.description: Great opportunity for a prime location in Monmouth, Oregon. Close to downtown Monmouth, Western Oregon University and parks. Perfect for a rental property, first home or downsize. Rooms are nice sized. 3rd bedroom can be used as a second living space. Kitchen has some original wood cabinets and built in shelving. Cute eating area. Fenced yard is loaded with grapes, figs, raspberries & blueberries. Come check it out!
